snippet.title: Best VGM 1076 - OutRun 2 - Life Was A Bore
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 911 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NGJp1-tPT54

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / Xbox
OutRun2 (2003) / OutRun 2006 : Coast 2 Coast
Life Was A Bore
Hiro, Fumio Itoh & Keisuke Tsukahara
